if(!require('pacman')) {install.packages('pacman')}
pacman::p_load(here, tidyverse, tidymodels, GGally, vip,
               naniar, rlang)


desp_data <- read_rds(here("import", "output", "baseline.rds")) %>% 
  filter(YEAR_EVENTO >= 2006 & YEAR_EVENTO <= 2022 &
           LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO != "SIGUE DESAPARECIDA" & DIFF_DIAS >= 0 &
           DIFF_DIAS < 32929) %>% 
  add_column(runif = runif(nrow(.))) %>% 
  rename(RANDOM = runif)
desp_data %>% 
  summarise(max = max(DIFF_DIAS, na.rm = T),
            min = min(DIFF_DIAS, na.rm = T),
            mean = mean(DIFF_DIAS, na.rm = T),
            sd = sd(DIFF_DIAS, na.rm = T))
## # A tibble: 1 × 4
##     max   min  mean    sd
##   <dbl> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl>
## 1  4595     0  88.6  276.

2. SPLIT DATA

## prepare data 
final_df <- desp_data %>% 
  arrange(YEAR_EVENTO) %>% 
  na.omit() %>% 
  mutate_if(is.character, as.factor) %>% 
  mutate(LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO = 
           factor(LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO, levels = c("VIVO", "MUERTO"))
         )
desp_data %>% count(LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO)
## # A tibble: 2 × 2
##   LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO     n
##   <chr>                  <int>
## 1 MUERTO                  1725
## 2 VIVO                   30105
set.seed(123)
splits  <- initial_time_split(final_df, strata = LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO)

desp_train <- training(splits)
desp_test <- testing(splits)
desp_train %>% count(YEAR_EVENTO, sort = T)

set.seed(234)
desp_validation <- validation_time_split(desp_train, strata = LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO)

Prepare models

### logistic regression 
glm_spec <- logistic_reg() %>%
  set_engine("glm") %>% 
  step_dummy(all_nominal_predictors()) %>% 
  step_zv(all_predictors()) %>% 
  step_normalize(all_predictors())

glm_spec
## Logistic Regression Model Specification (classification)
## 
## Computational engine: glm
### Decision tree
tree_spec <-
  decision_tree() %>%
  set_mode("classification") %>%
  set_engine("rpart") %>% 
  step_dummy(all_nominal_predictors()) %>% 
  step_zv(all_predictors()) %>% 
  step_normalize(all_predictors())

tree_spec
## Decision Tree Model Specification (classification)
## 
## Computational engine: rpart
## Random forest 
rf_spec <- rand_forest() %>%
  set_mode("classification") %>%
  set_engine("ranger", importance = "permutation")

rf_spec
## Random Forest Model Specification (classification)
## 
## Engine-Specific Arguments:
##   importance = permutation
## 
## Computational engine: ranger
xgb_spec <- boost_tree(
  trees = 1000
) %>%
  set_engine("xgboost") %>%
  set_mode("classification")

xgb_spec
## Boosted Tree Model Specification (classification)
## 
## Main Arguments:
##   trees = 1000
## 
## Computational engine: xgboost
desp_wf <- workflow() %>%
  add_formula(LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO ~ .)

desp_wf
## ══ Workflow ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
## Preprocessor: Formula
## Model: None
## 
## ── Preprocessor ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO ~ .

Fit models on traint/validation

glm_rs <- desp_wf %>%
  add_model(glm_spec) %>%
  fit_resamples(
    resamples = desp_validation,
    control = control_resamples(save_pred = TRUE),
    metrics = metric_set(roc_auc, accuracy, f_meas, bal_accuracy, sensitivity, specificity)
  )

glm_rs

Evaluate

GLM

collect_metrics(glm_rs)
## # A tibble: 6 × 6
##   .metric      .estimator  mean     n std_err .config             
##   <chr>        <chr>      <dbl> <int>   <dbl> <chr>               
## 1 accuracy     binary     0.980     1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
## 2 bal_accuracy binary     0.510     1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
## 3 f_meas       binary     0.990     1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
## 4 roc_auc      binary     0.955     1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
## 5 sensitivity  binary     1.00      1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
## 6 specificity  binary     0.02      1      NA Preprocessor1_Model1
collect_metrics(glm_rs) %>% 
  select(.metric, mean) %>% 
  filter(.metric == "sensitivity" | .metric == "specificity") %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = .metric,
              values_from = mean) %>% 
  mutate(gmean = sqrt(sensitivity*specificity))
## # A tibble: 1 × 3
##   sensitivity specificity gmean
##         <dbl>       <dbl> <dbl>
## 1        1.00        0.02 0.141
glm_rs %>%
  conf_mat_resampled()
## # A tibble: 4 × 3
##   Prediction Truth   Freq
##   <fct>      <fct>  <dbl>
## 1 VIVO       VIVO    2427
## 2 VIVO       MUERTO    49
## 3 MUERTO     VIVO       1
## 4 MUERTO     MUERTO     1
glm_auc <- glm_rs %>%
  collect_predictions() %>%
  group_by(id) %>%
  roc_curve(LOCALIZADO_VIVO_MUERTO, .pred_VIVO) %>%
  mutate(model = "GLM")

Compare AUCs

bind_rows(glm_auc, tree_auc, rf_auc, xgb_auc) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = 1 - specificity, y = sensitivity, col = model)) + 
  geom_path(linewidth = 1.5, alpha = 0.8) +
  geom_abline(lty = 3) + 
  coord_equal() + 
  scale_color_viridis_d(option = "turbo", end = .6) +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(title = "AUC comparison",
       subtitle = "On training and validation set")

Test set

desp_final <- desp_wf %>%
  add_model(rf_spec) %>%
  last_fit(splits,
           metrics = metric_set(roc_auc, accuracy, f_meas, bal_accuracy, sensitivity, specificity)
           )
